body:
I’ve been thinking about reviving my YouTube channel, but I’m going to take it in a very different direction. I’ve actually recorded the first video, which is… way out of my comfort zone, but I’m committing. 

Sometimes you have to face resistance to grow. That’s what my goal is here. Hopefully, I’ll be able to help others along the way.
